    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Alpine White over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This collector-tier example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline, mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the VANOS system has been proactively serviced, rod bearings addressed, and the rear subframe reinforced for long-term structural rigidity. The chassis retains its factory-fresh compliance with no bushing play, and the limited-slip differential operates silently. With zero pixel degradation in the cockpit and original paint showing deep luster, this is an investment-grade icon for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
