    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional example that redefines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, and its condition reflects a level of care rarely seen outside of a showroom. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory-fresh luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections; it glows with a mirror-like finish that highlights every body line. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury. The premium leather seats are supple, showing zero signs of wear or bolster compression, and still carry that distinct new-car aroma. Every button, switch, and digital display functions with crisp precision, and the high-grade carpeting has been protected by original mats since day one. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It has followed a rigorous, open-checkbook maintenance schedule with all service performed by certified technicians using only OEM parts. The engine bay is clean enough to serve as a display piece, and the undercarriage remains remarkably pristine. Included with the sale are all original keys, the complete owner's manual set, and a comprehensive binder of service records. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the vehicle you have been searching for.",
